news.headline: Stock Market News for Aug 4, 2025
news.summary: U.S. stocks tumbled on Friday, with the S&P 500 recording its biggest daily percentage decline in over two months, as hefty tariffs slapped on dozens of countries by President Donald Trump and an unexpectedly weak jobs report raised concerns over a weakening economy.
